Package model.prescriptions

Class Prescription

java.lang.Object
model.prescriptions.Prescription
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Copyable, SerializableCopyable
public class Prescription extends Object implements SerializableCopyable
An immutable representation a prescription for a medicine. A prescription consists of the drug ID, quantity, dosage and frequency of the medicine. The status of the prescription can be either PENDING or COMPLETED.
Since:
2024-10-27
